  <p>
    HelepApp (‚Äúwe‚Äù, ‚Äúour‚Äù, or ‚Äúus‚Äù), operated by <strong>Mankis LLC Co. Ltd</strong> in Douala, Cameroon,
    provides marketplace services for cleaning, home transfers, water supply, and delivery.
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Personal details: name, phone number, email, ID documents (for KYC verification).</li>
    <li>Payment data: MTN Mobile Money (MoMo) Cameroon transactions via Flutterwave or PawaPay, escrow records, payout receipts.</li>
    <li>Location data: GPS coordinates or address for service delivery and agent matching.</li>
    <li>Communication: in-app chat, emails, push and SMS notifications.</li>
    <li>Device & usage data: analytics, crash reports, and logs via Firebase.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use the Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Operate and manage bookings and escrow payments.</li>
    <li>Verify user identities through KYC for compliance and payout authorization.</li>
    <li>Send service updates via push notifications, SMS, and email.</li>
    <li>Handle dispute resolution and refund processes.</li>
    <li>Analyze and improve the platform‚Äôs performance and safety.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Escrow, Payments & Withdrawals</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Payments for services are held in escrow until completion or dispute resolution.</li>
    <li>Funds can only be withdrawn after an approved service transaction ‚Äî no wallet-only withdrawals are allowed.</li>
    <li>Payouts are sent to verified MTN MoMo Cameroon accounts after successful KYC and compliance checks.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Disputes & Refunds</h2>
  <p>
    If a customer reports a problem, HelepApp investigates and may hold funds in escrow until a resolution is reached.
    Refunds are processed via the same payment provider when applicable.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Firebase, Emails & Notifications</h2>
  <p>
    We use Firebase Cloud Messaging for push notifications, Firebase Analytics for performance data, and
    third-party email/SMS gateways for communications related to bookings, payments, and disputes.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Data Retention & Deletion</h2>
  <p>
    Data is stored as long as necessary for service delivery, compliance, and legal purposes. You can
    request deletion at any time by contacting <strong>support@helepapp.tech</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Security & Compliance</h2>
  <p>
    All payment and personal data are encrypted and securely stored. We comply with applicable data protection
    laws and MTN MoMo‚Äôs payment standards.
  </p>

